"niravadhi sudarsana bhakta-raksa kare
prag distam bhrtya-raksayam purusena mahatmana dadaha krtyam tam cakram kruddhahim iva pavakah
prthak cakara tat tejas cakram visnor akalpayat
trisulam capi rudrasya vajram indrasya cadhikam
daitya-danava-samhartuh sahasra-kiranatmakam
varayudho ''yam devesa sarvayudha-nibarhanah
sudarsano dvadasaro yo manah-sadrso jiva
arat sthita ami catra deva masas ca rasayah sistanam raksanarthaya samsthita rtavas tu sat
agnih somas tatha mitro varunas ca praja-patih indragni canyatho visve praja-pataya eva ca
hanumams catha balavan devo dhanvantaris tatha
tapamsy eva tapasas ca dvadasaite pratisthitah
caitradyah phalgunas tas ca masas tatra pratisthitah
tvam evam adaya vibho varayudham
satrum suranam jahi ma visankithah amogha eso ''mara-raja-pujito dhrto maya deha-gatas tapo-balat',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.2.144','cb','cb.antya.2','ЧБ Антья 2.144',144,NULL,'ye papistha vaisnavera paksa himsa kare sudarsana-agnite se papi pudi'' mare',NULL,NULL),('cb.antya.2.145','cb','cb.antya.2','ЧБ Антья 2.145',145,NULL,'visnu-cakra sudarsana raksaka thakite kara sakti ache bhakta-janere langhite"
